channel.title: How Big Is Your Autoer Army?
channel.description:
Well usually accounts get banned often for autoing and whatnot so we usually need to have a good amount ready and at hand...it is also very effiecient and makes it so that one account isnt there mining the same rock for 5 hours :)
I decided we should have a pole for whoever has the largest autoer army under their command.
Post the amount of autoers you have and we will have a bit of a contest to see who has the most
Also if your army follows any specific name like (autoer X1) you can post that but you dont have to because of confidentiality reasons
